commitResults.messageTitle: Renaming of chatbot, Greeting from chatbot and exit message
Improve skeletal version of Doobert so that it echos commands entered by the user, and exits when the user types the command "bye".
Add the ability to store whatever text entered by the user and display them back to the user when requested.
Add the ability to mark tasks as done and add the ability to change the status back to not done.
commitResults.messageBody:
Add Task class to keep track of tasks status.

Remove Storage class.
